  <h2>Flow</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Users (BDC/Sales/Service/Parts/Marketing) interact with copilots (web/voice).</li>
    <li>On-prem Caddy terminates TLS, proxies WebSocket to OpenAI Realtime.</li>
    <li>Adapters are read-only to CRM/DMS (e.g., VIN Solutions) in Phase-1.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Control points</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>System/meta prompts; redaction; deterministic uncertainty handling.</li>
    <li>Change mgmt via PR; test harness; prompt linting.</li>
    <li>Logs with PII redaction; no raw audio storage.</li>
  </ul>

  <h2>Network</h2>
  <ul>
    <li>Separate voice/servers VLAN; no SMB/RDP exposed.</li>
    <li>Inbound 80/443 only; egress allow-list to OpenAI, Twilio, Let’s Encrypt.</li>
  </ul>

